{"word":"ἀποξηραίνω","slug":"ἀποξηραίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποξηραίνω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to dry up</i> a river, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be dried up, run dry</i>, of rivers, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>generally <i>to dry completely</i>, <el>τὰς ναῦς</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}